  'Activates the following effects when there are 2 of this Kismet on the same pact page: Triggers the Main Active Skill 0.5s after using an Attack Horizontal Projectile Skill. Interval: 1s Triggers the Main Active Skill 1s after using an Attack Horizontal Projectile Skill. Interval: 1s Triggers the Main Active Skill 1.5s after using an Attack Horizontal Projectile Skill. Interval: 1s': '如果契约板上存在两个该天命，激活以下效果： 使用攻击直射投射物技能 0.5 秒后，触发核心主动技能，间隔 1 秒 使用攻击直射投射物技能 1 秒后，触发核心主动技能，间隔 1 秒 使用攻击直射投射物技能 1.5 秒后，触发核心主动技能，间隔 1 秒',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: +12%additional Attack Damage and Ailment Damage dealt by attacks when there are Elites within 10m nearby +50%Skill Area when there are no Elites within 10m nearby': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 周围 10 米内有 劲敌 时，额外 +12 % 攻击伤害与攻击造成的 异常伤害 周围 10 米内没有 劲敌 时， +50 % 技能范围',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:+12%additional Attack Damage and Ailment Damage dealt by attacks when there are Elites within 10m nearby+50%Skill Area when there are no Elites within 10m nearby': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 周围 10 米内有劲敌时，额外 +12% 攻击伤害与攻击造成的异常伤害周围 10 米内没有劲敌时，+50% 技能范围',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: When channeling Harmonious Field, triggers the Sentry Main Skill if there are no Sentries within 10m. Interval: 1s +30%Empower Skill Effect for Harmonious Field': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 引导调谐力场时，如果周围 10 米内没有哨卫，则触发哨卫核心技能，间隔 1 秒 +30 % 调谐力场的激发技能效果',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:When channeling Harmonious Field, triggers the Sentry Main Skill if there are no Sentries within 10m. Interval: 1s+30%Empower Skill Effect for Harmonious Field': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 引导调谐力场时，如果周围 10 米内没有哨卫，则触发哨卫核心技能，间隔 1 秒+30% 调谐力场的激发技能效果',
