  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: +12%additional Attack Damage when holding a One-Handed Weapon +12%additional Base Damage for Two-Handed Weapons': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 持单手武器时，额外 +12 % 攻击伤害 额外 +12 % 双手武器基础伤害',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:+12%additional Attack Damage when holding a One-Handed Weapon+12%additional Base Damage for Two-Handed Weapons': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 持单手武器时，额外 +12% 攻击伤害额外 +12% 双手武器基础伤害',
  'Activates the following effects when there are 2 of this Kismet on the same pact page: 15%chance to cause an explosion when defeating a Cursed enemy with an Attack or Spell, dealing True Damage equal to 250%of the defeated enemy\'s Max Life to enemies within a 5m radius +15%Skill Area': '如果契约板上存在两个该天命，激活以下效果： 攻击或法术击败受诅咒的敌人有 15% 几率爆炸，对半径 5 米内的敌人造成被击败的敌人最大生命 250% 的真实伤害 +15% 技能范围',
  '[Penetrating] When dealing Fire, Lightning, or Cold Damage, inflicts Fire Infiltration , Lightning Infiltration , or Cold Infiltration respectively. Upon inflicting damage, +8%additional Elemental Damage for each type of Infiltration Effect the enemy has +12%additional Spell Damage': '[入木三分] 造成火焰、闪电、冰冷伤害时，分别施加 火焰渗透 、 闪电渗透 、 冰冷渗透 造成伤害时，敌人每有一种渗透效果，额外 +8 % 元素伤害 额外 +12 % 法术伤害',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: For every stack of Max Spell Burst , +4%additional Spell Damage, up to +16%additional Spell Damage': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 每有 1 层 法术迸发 上限，额外 +4 % 法术伤害，最多额外 +16 % 法术伤害',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:For every stack of Max Spell Burst, +4%additional Spell Damage, up to +16%additional Spell Damage': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 每有 1 层法术迸发上限，额外 +4% 法术伤害，最多额外 +16% 法术伤害',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: Eliminates enemies with less than 12%Life and at least 30 stack(s) of Wilt when dealing damage': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 造成伤害时，淘汰生命值低于 12 % 且至少拥有 30 层凋零的敌人',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:Eliminates enemies with less than 12%Life and at least 30 stack(s) of Wilt when dealing damage': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 造成伤害时，淘汰生命值低于 12% 且至少拥有 30 层凋零的敌人',
  'Activates the following effects when there are 2 of this Kismet on the same pact page: +15%additional damage for Attack Horizontal Projectiles +5%additional Attack Speed for Mobility Skills if Attack Horizontal Projectiles have dealt damage to distant enemies recently': '如果契约板上存在两个该天命，激活以下效果： 攻击直射投射物额外 +15%伤害 若最近攻击直射投射物对远处敌人造成伤害，位移技能额外 +5% 攻击速度',
  'Activates the following effects when there are 2 of this Kismet on the same pact page: +3%additional Ultimate Damage and Ailment Damage dealt by Ultimate (multiplies) for all Spirit Magi for every Ultimate used by a Spirit Magus recently. Stacks up to 3 times': '如果契约板上存在两个该天命，激活以下效果： 魔灵最近每使用一次终极技能，使所有魔灵额外 +3% 终极技能伤害和终极技能造成的异常伤害（叠乘），可以叠加 3 层',
  'When Command is lower than -40 , Nearby Synthetic Troop Minions deal +25%additional Projectile Damage to enemies in Proximity , and this damage reduces with the distance traveled by the Projectiles Minions\' Horizontal Projectiles cannot Penetrate': '统御值 不超过 -40 时，周围的智械召唤物对 近处 的敌人额外 +25 % 投射物伤害，随距离递减 召唤物的直射投射物无法穿透',
  'When Burst Charge Recovery Speed is at least (230-250)%of the base value, reaching the Max Spell Burst Charge triggers the Main Skill on the nearest enemy within 25m and attempts to activate the Main Spell Skill\'s Spell Burst -30%Movement Speed': '迸发充能回复速度不低于基础值的 (230-250) % 时， 法术迸发 充能达到上限对 25 米内最近的敌人触发核心技能，并尝试激活核心法术技能的 法术迸发 -30 % 移动速度',
  'Activates the following effects when there are 2 of this Kismet on the same pact page: Additionally increases damage by 2%(stacks) for every unique Kismet installed Reduces your damage taken by 1%(multiplies) for every unique Kismet installed': '如果契约板上存在两个该天命，激活以下效果： 每安装一个不同名天命，额外伤害提高 2% （叠加） 每安装一个不同名天命，使你受到的伤害降低 1%（叠乘）',
  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: 2.5%additional Minion Damage per Synthetic Troop Minion you own': '为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 每拥有一个智械召唤物，额外 2.5 % 召唤物伤害',
