  'Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel:+12%additional Spell Damage when you have Spell Aggression': '为巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 拥有法术激进时，额外 +12% 法术伤害',
