  'Frozen enemies have a (10-15)%chance to explode when defeated, dealing True Damage equal to (80-100)%of their Max Life to enemies within a 6 m radius': '击败被 冰封 的敌人时 (10-15) % 几率爆炸，对半径 6 米内的敌人造成被击败的敌人最大生命 (80-100) % 的真实伤害',
  '[True Flame] When an enemy is Ignited , 60%of the additional bonus to Damage Over Time taken from Affliction is also applied to your Fire Hit Damage': '[真实之焰] 敌人被 点燃 时， 加剧 对其受到的持续伤害额外加成的 60 % 同样作用于你的击中火焰伤害',
  'Reaps (1.3-1.5) s of Damage Over Time from enemies within 10 m that have full Affliction. The effect has a 1 s Recovery Time against the same target': '10 米内敌人加剧值达到上限时，收割其具有的 (1.3–1.5) 秒持续伤害，该效果对同一目标有 1 秒回复时间',
  'While Warcry is active, refresh the cooldown of the Warcry Skill whenever a number of enemies equal to the number of Warcry buff stacks are defeated': '战吼持续期间，每击败战吼增益层数的数量的敌人，刷新战吼技能的冷却时间',
  '+(30-40)%additional Lightning Damage against enemies+(30-40)%additional Max Lightning Damage to an enemy when they have at least (6-10) stack(s) of': '对的敌人，额外 +(30–40)% 闪电伤害敌人至少拥有 (6–10) 层时，额外 +(30–40)% 对其造成的最大闪电伤害',
