  'enemies defeated by you have a (40-50)%chance to explode, dealing True Damage equal to (16-20)%of their Max Life to enemies within a 6 m radius': '被你击败的敌人有 (40–50)% 几率爆炸，对半径 6 米内的敌人造成被击败的敌人最大生命 (16–20)% 的真实伤害',
